## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible challenges organizations face in valuing diversity and inclusion. Additionally, the information is limited to the perspectives and experiences shared in the selected sources, which may not be universally applicable. Further research, including empirical studies and organizational case studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of these challenges.